Organizing Internal Packages

---
title: Organizing Internal Packages
description: Organizing Internal Packages
globs:
  - "src/**/"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Each package has its own directory under src/, with a clear, lowercase name.
- Each package’s __init__.py file declares the public API via __all__.
- Avoid circular dependencies by extracting shared logic into dedicated modules.
- Keep code modular by grouping related functionality into separate packages.
